1. *Sačekaj* me ispred prodavnice. (Wait for me in front of the store.)
2. Moramo *sačekati* odgovor pre nego što donesemo odluku. (We have to wait for the answer before we make a decision.)
3. Ja ću *sačekati* ovde dok ti završiš sastanak. (I'll wait here while you finish the meeting.)
4. Molim vas, *sačekajte* malo dok proverim informacije. (Please wait a bit while I check the information.)
5. *Sačekajmo* da se gužva malo smanji pa ćemo krenuti. (Let's wait for the crowd to thin out a bit and then we'll leave.)
6. Nije pošteno da *sačekujemo* druge, trebalo bi da krenemo. (It's not fair to wait for others, we should go.)
7. Oni su *sačekali* da se sunce pojavi pre nego što su krenuli na izlet. (They waited for the sun to come out before they set off on their trip.)
8. Ne mogu *sačekati* da vidim šta si pripremio za ručak. (I can't wait to see what you've prepared for lunch.)
9. *Sačekajmo* da se situacija smiri pre nego što donosimo odluke. (Let's wait for the situation to calm down before making decisions.)
10. Nisam mogao *sačekati* da joj kažem koliko mi nedostaje. (I couldn't wait to tell her how much I miss her.)